1
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,480
Let's do a run-through first.

2
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,240
Come on.

3
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,080
Anan starts.

4
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:52,640
I'll start.

5
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:53,320
Come on.

6
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:55,600
Five, six, seven, go.

7
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,160
Da.

8
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:10,640
Come on.

9
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:11,360
This is right.

10
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,420
Come on. Like this.

11
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:17,250
How about...

12
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,400
...we do it again?

13
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:21,560
Ameng, remember.

14
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,400
The problem just now was still the speed.

15
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,560
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

16
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,120
Steady.

17
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,520
One more time.

18
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,320
One more time.

19
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,240
One more time.

20
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:30,480
Come on.

21
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,539
Let's do it.

22
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,320
Come on.

23
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,759
Five, six, seven, go.

24
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,360
Come on. Come in and have a seat.

25
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,360
I heard the food here is really good.

26
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,480
There's even a live band.

27
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,560
When will Qiuqiu come out?

28
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,490
Can the drum shop still be used?

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,880
I heard you started a band.

30
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,660
Just the three of them?

31
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,940
They don't look reliable.

32
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,900
Won't it be a waste of your talent?

33
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,730
Don't worry.

34
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,280
We just don't have a place to practice.

35
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,210
The three of them

36
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,560
are fine.

37
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,850
You know where the place is.

38
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,930
Use it however you like.

39
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,560
Thanks.

40
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:50,200
I'll give you ten percent off your lesson fees.

41
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,760
Just schedule a few more sessions for 'Nizhan'.

42
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,520
You got it.

43
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,840
I'm off.

44
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,440
Awesome.

45
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,560
This warehouse is amazing.

46
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:31,120
Come on. Let's get to work.

47
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,680
Come on.

48
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,520
Stop playing. Get to work.

49
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,040
Get to work.

50
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,840
Hurry up and work.

51
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,400
Okay.

52
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,340
Get to work.

53
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,800
Qiuqiu, do something about him. Get to work.

54
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,040
Get to work. Look at this.

55
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:47,480
Do something about him.

56
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,280
My bad. Come here, quick.

57
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,400
Get to work.

58
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,600
Hurry up and work.

59
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,040
Qiuqiu, look.

60
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:06,520
Almost there.

61
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,600
Anan,

62
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:17,930
look at this.

63
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,519
Done.

64
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,680
Impressive.

65
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:21,839
Try it out.

66
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,760
Come and try it.

67
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,850
That's about it.

68
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,159
Let's run through it.

69
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:38,680
Ready?

70
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,570
Drums first.

71
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,610
I have a class at 7. I'm heading out.

72
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,780
I'll walk Qiuqiu home. It's on my way.

73
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,420
Let me walk you.

74
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,440
Let's go.

75
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,400
Bye. See you tomorrow.

76
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,200
Bye.

77
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,610
Qiuqiu is so fierce.

78
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,980
And you still like her?

79
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,000
I...

80
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,160
I think she's great.

81
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:06,040
She looks so cool when she plays the drums.

82
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:08,520
Fine.

83
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,360
You don't dare to confess anyway.

84
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,960
So just focus on practicing.

85
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,960
Good music doesn't lie.

86
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,320
Then would you lie?

87
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,240
Are you crazy?

88
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,000
Actually,

89
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,640
you still want to make music, don't you?

90
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,280
To make music,

91
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,360
you have to do many things unrelated to it.

92
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,620
Thumb, index, middle.

93
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,930
It's too tiring.

94
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:09,400
Forearm vertical and tilted.

95
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,370
Give it a try.

96
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,890
Yes, just like that.

97
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,840
Relax your shoulders.

98
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,960
Don't hunch your shoulders.

99
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,240
Keep your shoulders down.

100
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,320
Forearm vertical.

101
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,720
Shoulders down.

102
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,740
Forearm vertical.

103
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,120
It hurts.

104
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,960
Where?

105
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,680
It's a cramp. Is it here?

106
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,410
It's a cramp.

107
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,080
No.

108
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,640
Is it better?

109
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,360
It's perfect.

110
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,640
The posture is perfect after the cramp.

111
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,000
Hold it. Don't move.

112
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,600
Are you even human?

113
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,680
It's out of tune.

114
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,280
Liu Ma,

115
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:11,120
you can tell even when you're distracted?

116
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,920
Play it again.

117
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,160
Even eagles aren't trained this hard.

118
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,320
No wonder you're called Liu Ma.

119
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,890
You're up early.

120
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,000
Did you two stay up all night?

121
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,919
Ameng,

122
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,160
show them.

123
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,800
Show us.

124
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,560
So that's what a bass sounds like.

125
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,560
I knew I was right.

126
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,610
The sanxian is similar to the bass.

127
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,170
It's easy to pick up.

128
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,240
Piece of cake.

129
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:33,080
Master taught me well.

130
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,640
Brother.

131
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,840
Brother.

132
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,050
Let's wrap it up.

133
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,560
Wrap it up.

134
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,400
Let's go home.

135
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,760
Anan, turn off the lights.

136
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,320
Okay.

137
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,640
Let's go.

138
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,360
Go.

139
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,320
That was good, Qiuqiu.

140
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,480
No problem at all.

141
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,570
Something's wrong.

142
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,040
What's wrong? Which bar?

143
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,460
I mean something's off with Anan.

144
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,080
He's never been late before.

145
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,880
Didn't you see him when you left?

146
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,960
To keep his mom from finding out,

147
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,160
we leave separately.

148
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:48,720
Hello. The number you have dialed is switched off.
